I like this for two reasons. First, I always love very short SCPs, the ones that get to the point and don't add too much fluff. Second, I like it because there aren't dragons or demons or a black hole on the other end. It lets out at a theater in fucking Michigan. It's realistically unrealistic. It does have some tone issues, specifically in the second Description paragraph, but I like it all in all.







